A good time was had by all , a special cheesecake with flaming liquor finished up the evening.

A good choice for our parents first restaurant experience since March . Estancia did a great job with social distancing and mask wearing when not at your table. The famous salad bar was either selected and brought to the table or you could go up and point to what you wanted for a server to create your plate. We did both... the steak was as good as ever, as was the chimichuri sauce .
A good time was had by all , a special cheesecake with flaming liquor finished up the evening.
